nodes.text: "Divide and Conquer" is an issue of the comic book series Star Wars Rebels Animation-Magazine. It was first published in English in the October 2019 issue of the Australian magazine K-Zone.

In the final panel of the comic, Phoenix Cell is represented with CR90 corvettes, Sphyrna-class Hammerhead corvettes, and a Pelta-class frigate. However, since the comic takes place after the episode "The Protector of Concord Dawn," the cell's Pelta-class frigate was destroyed in Star Wars Rebels: The Siege of Lothal.
